{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/extras/Box.png?t=1738337040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Seventeen years ago, a band of mercenaries took in Mike, orphaned as a baby. Now, on his first mission, things go sideways\u2014and soon, he's caught in a conflict where right and wrong aren\u2019t so clear.</i>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/extras/Divider.png?t=1738337040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tackle the problems you encounter as you see fit,  or become the problem yourself! </strong>Rely on physical prowess, logical thinking, or intuition by rolling dice in true tabletop RPG style! Do what you feel is right \u2014 or don't. The choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/extras/Skill_Check.gif?t=1738337040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/extras/UniqueSkills.png?t=1738337040\" /><strong>Shape your character with a unique blend of skills</strong> that encompass not only physical and mental attributes but also the ability to channel the spirit world. Whether you follow your morals or give in to instincts will shape how you see the world\u2014and how it sees you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/extras/skills.gif?t=1738337040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/extras/MakeFriends.png?t=1738337040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Earn the trust of those you encounter, gain their respect and friendship, or manipulate them with lies and deception.</strong> Everyone has a truth\u2014it\u2019s up to you to uncover yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/extras/Make_friends.gif?t=1738337040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/extras/ShapeYourStory.png?t=1738337040\" /><strong>Even the smallest decision can change your story.</strong> Deal with the consequences and make the most of your situation. The world is your oyster\u2014you decide whether to swallow it whole, chew it, garnish it with lemon juice, or pair it with Champagne mignonette sauce.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/extras/Divider.png?t=1738337040\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/extras/JoinTheDiscord2.png?t=1738337040\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738337040","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/page.bg.jpg?t=1738337040","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/a631a4e2d3d041693526abf987f9fbebe7d9c5f2/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738337040","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780990/a631a4e2d3d041693526abf987f9fbebe7d9c5f2/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738337040","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3291020,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_